ZH: 这是一张处方，你可以凭它去医院开药。
EN: This is a prescription, you can use it to get medicine at the hospital.

ZH: 我的处方被医生签了字，可以去药店购买药物了。
EN: My prescription has been signed by the doctor, I can go to the pharmacy to buy the medicine.

ZH: 这个药方是中医开的，需要到药店熬制。
EN: This herbal prescription was prescribed by a traditional Chinese medicine practitioner, and it needs to be prepared at the pharmacy.

ZH: 医生给了我一个处方，但我还没去拿药。
EN: The doctor gave me a prescription, but I haven't picked up the medicine yet.

ZH: 这个处方上写得很清楚，你可以直接拿到药店里去买药。
EN: The prescription is written clearly, you can take it directly to the pharmacy to buy medicine.

ZH: 我的处方被医生开了两周的药量。
EN: My prescription has a two-week supply of medication prescribed by the doctor.

ZH: 这张处方上写了我每天吃药的剂量和时间。
EN: This prescription specifies the dosage and timing of the medication I need to take every day.

ZH: 请将这张处方保存好，以备将来购药使用。
EN: Please keep this prescription safe for future reference when purchasing medication.

ZH: 需要处方才能购买某些处方药。
EN: Some prescription medications require a prescription to purchase.

ZH: RX代表“处方”的意思，常常出现在药品标签上。
EN: RX stands for "prescription" and is often found on medication labels.

ZH: 这是医生为你开的新处方，请及时拿药。
EN: This is a new prescription the doctor prescribed for you, please pick up the medicine in a timely manner.

ZH: 确保按照医生的处方服用药物。
EN: Make sure to take the medication according to the doctor's prescription.

ZH: 这种药只能凭处方购买，不能在超市买到。
EN: This medicine can only be purchased with a prescription and is not available at supermarkets.

ZH: 如果你丢失了处方，可以向医生重新开一张。
EN: If you lose your prescription, you can ask the doctor to issue a new one for you.

ZH: 请将处方单放在明显的地方，以防忘记购买药物。
EN: Please keep the prescription note in a visible place to avoid forgetting to buy the medication.

ZH: 这个药房接受电子处方，你可以请医生直接发给他们。
EN: This pharmacy accepts electronic prescriptions, you can ask the doctor to send it directly to them.

ZH: 我需要去开一份处方给我的朋友。
EN: I need to get a prescription for my friend.

ZH: 药师会根据处方准备药物。
EN: The pharmacist will prepare the medication based on the prescription.

ZH: 请仔细阅读处方上的用药说明。
EN: Please read the medication instructions on the prescription carefully.

ZH: 这种药需要处方才能购买，并且只能在医院取得。
EN: This medication requires a prescription to purchase and can only be obtained at hospitals.
